                        <interp inst="t18410920-name-832" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN HALL</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable D</hi> 64.) At a quarter-past ten o'clock I was coming along Holborn—I heard a cry of "Stop thief"—I saw the prisoner running, and a mob after him—he went down Middle-row—I saw Smith collar him, and take the handkerchief from him.</p>
